com.tsgrp.migration.mapping.proc

Interface MappingProcessor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ApplyCompoundMappingProcessor, ApplyMappingProcessor, DefaultMappingProcessor, NoopMappingProcessor

    public interface MappingProcessor
    The common interface for a mapping processor. A mapping processor takes a Node as input applies any configured attribute mappings or transformations, and returns a resulting Node
